OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FStruggling pubs are piling pressure on
OL,7,Fthe government to re-examine an
OL,8,Fimpending rise in business rates, with
OL,9,Fmany saying their costs will rise by
OL,10,Ftens of thousands per year.
OL,12,FMinisters are facing growing Labour
OL,13,Fbackbench concerns over the pub
OL,14,Fsector, amid the withdrawal of a Covid-
OL,15,Fera tax break announced at the budget.
OL,17,FIn November, Rachel Reeves confirmed
OL,18,Fthe changes to how business rates `
OL,19,Fthe tax affecting commercial
OL,20,Fproperties ` will be calculated,
OL,21,Fincluding a new multiplier from April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
