OL,6,FThe chancellor also announced the
OL,7,Fphasing out of a Covid-era relief
OL,8,Foffered to businesses, a discount of
OL,9,F40%, from the same month.
OL,11,FThe Campaign for Real Ale (Camra) has
OL,12,Fwarned the "extortionate increase in
OL,13,Fbills" due to the hike in rates "is
OL,14,Fgoing to crush our pubs".
