OL,6,FLabour MP Rachael Maskell urged Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer at Prime Minister's
OL,8,FQuestions to review the proposals,
OL,9,Fwarning that many businesses in her
OL,10,Fconstituency of York Central will have
OL,11,Fto close down as a result of the
OL,12,Fimpending changes.
OL,14,FReeves had pledged the lowest
OL,15,Fpermanent business rates since 1991
OL,16,Ffor more than 750,000 retail, leisure
OL,17,Fand hospitality businesses, but
OL,18,Fexperts argued the changes will result
OL,19,Fin a sharp annual increase in costs.
