OL,6,FUKHospitality analysis found the
OL,7,Faverage pub's business rates will
OL,8,Fincrease 15% this year - an extra
OL,9,F#1,400 - even with the reduced
OL,10,Fmultiplier and when taking into
OL,11,Faccount transitional relief.
OL,13,FOne west London pub owner told ITV
OL,14,FNews his costs will increase from
OL,15,Faround #2,500 to more than #20,000 per
OL,16,Fyear, while another said he will have
OL,17,Fto pay 92% more in business rates than
OL,18,Fthe year before.
