OL,6,FBusiness rates are taxes charged on
OL,7,Fmost non-domestic properties, like
OL,8,Fcouncil taxes paid on homes.
OL,10,FThey're calculated by multiplying the
OL,11,Frateable value of a property by a
OL,12,Fmultiplier.
OL,14,FThe multiplier will decrease from 49p
OL,15,Fin the pound to 43p.
