OL,3,CPub owner says business rates changes
OL,4,Cwill cost him #20,000 more per year
OL,6,FAfter the initial Budget announcement,
OL,7,Fthe Treasury published new rateable
OL,8,Fvalues for properties, which will
OL,9,Faffect how much property tax
OL,10,Fbusinesses will pay from the next
OL,11,Ffinancial year.
OL,13,FDespite business rates going down, the
OL,14,Frateable value of some properties will
OL,15,Fincrease.
OL,17,FThis means some business owners will
OL,18,Fbe paying a smaller percentage on a
OL,19,Fhigher value - thus, some will pay
OL,20,Fmore than they did previously despite
OL,21,Fthe multiplier decrease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
