OL,6,FFor example, a business currently
OL,7,Fpaying 49% of #10,000 might find
OL,8,Fthemselves paying 43% of #20,000 from
OL,9,FApril next year. That's an extra
OL,10,F#3,700 per year.
OL,12,FPhasing out of Covid relief
OL,14,FA third factor affecting business
OL,15,Fcosts is the phasing out of financial
OL,16,Fsupport for businesses introduced
OL,17,Fduring Covid and replaced with smaller
OL,18,Fsupport.
